      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブの前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――営業時間中の喫茶ラビットハウス",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca001.m4a",
      "text": "この街にいる間は、私のことをお姉ちゃんだと思って\n頼ってくれていいからね",
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、お姉ちゃんに任せなさい！　この街のことも\nラビットハウスのこともなんでも聞いてね！",
      "startTime": 13.6999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn001.m4a",
      "text": "またあんなこと言ってます……",
      "startTime": 17.2090069372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ココアさんって、よく「お姉ちゃんって呼んで」って\n言ってるけど、いつもあんな調子なの？",
      "startTime": 23.6464735404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。可愛い子を見るとすぐ\nお姉ちゃんになりたがります。見境がないです",
      "startTime": 30.0999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "でもあの二人、すっかり打ち解けてるね\n千紗さんもココアさんが相手だと話しやすいみたい",
      "startTime": 38.1947046596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？",
      "startTime": 42.1280381439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、二人は意外と相性がいいのかも",
      "startTime": 43.8338975825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……ココアさんと千紗さんが……",
      "startTime": 48.4338975825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn005.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしてでしょう……）\n（さっきから胸の奥がもやもやします……）",
      "startTime": 57.5333295186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……チノちゃん？",
      "startTime": 61.8980942961,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}